  "article_text": "Welcome to the Star Atlas weekly recap from the Intergalactic Herald. Below is what happened with Star Atlas this past week.\nWe are looking for guests to be on our podcast. The podcast is a discussion of the past week’s news about Star Atlas. If you are interested in being on the podcast, please contact us.\nWe are launching a Star Atlas merch store. Please check it out at Intergalactic Gear.\nWe are creating a “non-guild” guild. If you are interested in learning more, please go to Intergalactic Coalition.\nIf you would like to support our efforts, donations can be sent to intergalacticherald.sol\nSolana Crossroads – The Solana Conference [Day 2]\nStar Atlas gave a presentation at the Solana Crossroads conference.\nA New Release on the Horizon — Star Atlas Crew Packs Coming in Q2 2024\nStar Atlas published an article about a pre-release of Crew Packs.\nStar Atlas: Solana Crossroads Event!\nBeyond the Horizon posted a video about the Solana Crossroads conference.\nStar Atlas: SAGE Starbased Changes\nBeyond the Horizon posted a video about the SAGE Starbased changes.\nSTAR ATLAS #234 CREW PACKS HAVE ARRIVED!\nMetaVerse Explorer posted a video about the Star Altas Crew Packs.\nMetaverse Nomads #146 – Star Atlas @ Solana Crossroads / Platinum 10 Crew Pack\nMetaverse Nomads posted a video replay of their weekly Star Atlas livestream.\nWEEKLY STAR ATLAS NEWSLETTER #129\nAephia published their weekly Star Atlas newsletter.\nThe Atlas Brew #111\nStar Atlas TV posted a replay of the latest Atlas Brew.\nSOLD OUT! — Star Atlas Sells All Five Thousand Pre-Sale Crew Pack Bundles in Less Than 24 Hours After Solana Crossroads Event\nStar Atlas published an article about announcements from the Solana Crossroads conference.\nStar Atlas And Topper Partnership\nBeyond the Horizon posted a video about a partnership with Topper.",
